subject: You’re Invited! Let’s Celebrate Together 🎈
body:
Hi OOD!

I’m throwing a party and it wouldn’t be the same without you there! Come
join us for a night of fun, laughter, and good vibes.

*Here are the details:*

*📅 Date:* April 20, 2025
*⏰ Time:* 8 PM
*📍 Location:* Virginia, US

Bring your energy, your dance moves, and maybe a friend or two.

Can’t wait to see you there!

Cheers,

Sireesha
